BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313766606@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260315T030933Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260315T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260315T130000
SUMMARY:Stop Struggling to Survive\, How to Expect Miracles to Thrive
DESCRIPTION:Raleigh & Triangle Activities Meetup Group\nLife is unnecessar
 ily difficult when we hold onto something that isn’t right for us. Inste
 ad of just letting go what doesn’t work\, we may think that life itself 
 is the problem and it’s just too hard. But the Universe isn’t broken a
 nd the divine Source is always with us. In fact\, the entire system of exi
 stence is designed to give everyone whatever they need to thrive in joy fo
 rever. So\, if all Creation is built for healthy happiness\, why is there 
 so much struggle and suffering in the human world? Join us this Sunday Mar
 ch 15\, 2026\, for a free empowering talk on the origins of suffering and 
 why miraculous gifts of life are the default that we need to be expecting.
 \n\nIt’s vital to realize that everything can be used for positive or ne
 gative outcomes. Positive is the direction of more love\, with all the hel
 p you need to make life easy\, fun and wonderful. Negative is the directio
 n of less love\, with non-solutions that will cause you to fail followed b
 y lies that say it's all your fault\, you're so bad\, it's hopeless\, give
  up. The goal of negativity is simple: hurt you any way it can so that you
  will stop functioning. There are many ways to break something\, and often
  only one best way to do it right. Life is direct and efficient this way\,
  while negativity is obvious in its failings.\n\nA negative society doesn'
 t want strong individuals\, it wants weak followers and slaves. That's bec
 ause negativity is so weak that it doesn't trust any higher power than its
 elf. In the Bible story\, Lucifer wanted to be God\, so God gave him a pit
  of hell to rule. Many suckers followed Lucifer down into the endless suff
 ering that comes from refusing higher assistance. Religion is just early p
 sychology\, so Lucifer shows the personality disorders that drive cruel na
 rcissistic behaviors. This usually comes from childhood abuse that causes 
 a person to shut down their feelings and go into a survival mode of opport
 unistic controlling and bullying\, all within a continual victimhood. In a
  negative society there are many roles to play for who is the weak victim 
 of violence and who looks powerful. To forgive with compassion\, we can se
 e through the dramas to realize everyone is suffering inside.\n\nSince the
  negativity on Earth is so advanced these days\, with many layers of war\,
  pollution\, deprivation and corruption\, it is easy to think that life it
 self is bad and must be fixed somehow. There are many well-intentioned peo
 ple who exhaust themselves in dramatic battles for justice and struggles t
 o make the world a better place. Justice warriors might succeed if it were
  true that life is broken\, but it's not. All the divine guidance we will 
 ever need to live well is always offered to us. The real villain behind su
 ffering is false negative beliefs. When you misuse what you have due to wr
 ong ideas\, you fail with increasing pain and suffering. It's like having 
 a fabulous car and not driving it correctly. Some people never get out of 
 the driveway of life\, others just keep crashing on the highway. The solut
 ion is simple. Learn how life really works so you can drive yourself to pa
 radise!\n\nTo prepare for this meetup\, recall where you struggle and suff
 er in your life. Pain is separation from what we need to be happy. Problem
 s cause temporary pain until a solution is found. But false beliefs make u
 s blind to solutions\, causing endless pain which is suffering. Human bein
 gs automatically adapt to suffering and find ways to survive\, including a
 ddictions to numb the pain and toxic relationships to stay distracted and 
 have someone to blame. Negative society makes many rules and judgments for
  who is bad to be punished and who is good to be rewarded.\n\nStruggle is 
 unnatural\, since the true nature of the Universe is to freely give us mir
 acles of divine guidance and solutions. Miracles would come to us all the 
 time\, but usually people only allow them when they’re desperate enough.
  Can you recall a time when you felt hopeless\, ready to smash things in f
 rustration or collapse in despair\, and then suddenly a miracle appeared? 
 Celebrate that feeling\, let it grow in the truth of your own life!\n\nAft
 er check-ins to share and relate\, I’ll explain where problems come from
  and how to handle the emotions like self-pity and shame that keep us stuc
 k in suffering. We’ll learn to identify false negative beliefs and take 
 steps to release them for the truths of an easy love-filled life. We’ll 
 conclude with a guided meditation to meet with our higher self and exchang
 e gifts of the love that makes life truly wonderful.\n\nWelcome! Our Inner
  Selves Mastery spiritual support group is free online every Sunday 11am-1
 30pm EDT\, with the last 30 minutes for a guided meditation. If you can’
 t stay you can get the recording. You can signup here for this meeting and
  visit www.signupISM.com for all events\, newsletter\, videos\, and more.\
 n\nBest wishes\,\nCarl Johann Schroeder\nInner Selves Mastery\nspiritual t
 eaching and coaching\nquick-links at [www.signupISM.com](http://www.signup
 ISM.com)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/raleigh-triangle-activities/events/31
 3766606/
